text: St. Joseph College, Barranquilla, (Colegio San Jose), is located in the San Jose section of Barranquilla, Colombia. It was founded by the Society of Jesus in 1918 and currently covers kindergarten through baccalaureate. ==References== Category:Jesuit secondary schools Category:Catholic schools in Colombia Category:Educational institutions established in 1918
title: St. Joseph College, Barranquilla
